lead_paragraph: Dillon Brooks hit a 3-pointer with 0.8 seconds left to give No. 21 Oregon an 89-87 victory over No. 2 UCLA on Wednesday night in the Pac-12 opener for both teams.

headline.print_headline: No. 21 Oregon Upsets No. 2 UCLA on Brooks' 3-Pointer
